        "text": "=Analyze these AI news articles:\n\n{{ $json.news }}\n\nSelect the top 5 most important developments.\n\nFor each provide:\n- Title\n- Summary\n- Why it matters\n- Link\n\nThen provide:\n1. Biggest AI Trend Today\n2. Most Important Research\n3. Recommended Action for AI Engineers",
